# Sprint 62 — release tarball artifacts produced by `pnpm release:pack-artifacts`
# (uploaded by CI as `plccopilot-release-tarballs`). Local runs leave them
# under .release-artifacts/ for manual inspection; never commit them.
.release-artifacts/
